commandDescription.en-US: Tells you where to watch community speedruns of the game
commandDescription.fr: Te dit où regarder des speedruns communautaires du jeu
commandDescription.pt-BR: Te diz onde assistir as speedruns da comunidade do jogo

help.en-US: Type $<commandMention> to know where to watch community speedruns of the game
help.fr: Tape $<commandMention> pour savoir où regarder des speedruns communautaires du jeu
help.pt-BR: Digite $<commandMention> pra saber onde assistir as speedruns da comunidade do jogo

reply.en-US:
You can watch community speedruns there:
$<linkList>
reply.fr:
Tu peux regarder des speedruns communautaires là :
$<linkList>
reply.pt-BR:
Você pode assistir speedruns da comunidade aqui:
$<linkList>
